148
00:12:37,804 --> 00:12:41,826
I think it's a way, and we speak about it all the time, to be proactive.

149
00:12:42,206 --> 00:12:53,413
You know, what happened a couple weeks ago with the Winthrop Street, George Street intersection, that was a, it needed to be in front of the council, but that was a reactive situation where the city reacted

